(4200000, "Look who's there! $N, a brave soul that wills to sacrifice themselves just to prove their mastery!$BI am Gorr, and I can put you in Hardcore Mode. When you dieâ€¦ it's permanent. Your soul will never return to your body! Don't seek help: only Hardcore characters can play with you. Others won't be even able to buff you, heal you, or help you killing creatures! You can use only Hardcore Auction House, and can trade only with Hardcore characters", NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1),
(4200001, "Are you sure you want to do that? You can never opt-out of Hardcore Mode and your death is permanent and cannot be appealed.", NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1);
